title: Organic Chemistry Laboratory
description: Identification of unknown organic compounds by a combination of chemical and physical techniques. Enrollment is limited to majors in the Department of Chemistry and Biochemistry unless space is available. Program or materials fees may apply. Prerequisites: CHEM 43A, 43AM, 143A, 143AM, or 143AH and CHEM 40B, 40BH, 41B, 140B, or 140BH.
